					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Hahahahah, I can't fucking believe it. This is too perfect.</p> <p>I was gonna begrudgingly upvote, but somehow you took my throwaway idea about a toilet that made people think it was an ATM, and then somehow you turned it into a toilet that destroys all posessions, is referential to an existing artwork, and then made it pointlessly harmful to boot.</p> <p><em>whoosh</em></p> 
